  (90, 'Nightmares', 'Rod', 'Epic', 'No', 'Null', '21', '284,000 gp', 'Null', 'Craft Rod, Craft Epic Rod, nightmare, permanency, wail of the banshee', 'Null', 'Null', '&lt;div topic=&quot;Nightmares&quot; level=&quot;8&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Nightmares:&lt;/b&gt; Anyone who comes within 20 feet of the wielder of this rod feels a grave sense of unease. Each person so affected must make a Will save (DC 17) or suffer the effects of a &lt;i&gt;nightmare&lt;/i&gt; spell the next time he or she falls asleep. The wielder is immune to this effect. Three times per day, the wielder can utter a command word that causes the rod to emit a horrid, inhuman scream. Up to twenty of the closest creatures within a 30-foot radius who hear this terrible wail believe that their worst nightmares have become reality and suffer the effects of a &lt;i&gt;wail of the banshee&lt;/i&gt; spell (DC 23).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Caster Level:&lt;/i&gt; 21st; &lt;i&gt;Prerequisites:&lt;/i&gt; Craft Rod, Craft Epic Rod, &lt;i&gt;nightmare&lt;/i&gt;,  &lt;i&gt;permanency&lt;/i&gt;,  &lt;i&gt;wail of the banshee; Market Price:&lt;/i&gt; 284,000 gp.&lt;/p&gt;
