  (376, 'Chameleon Power', 'Ring', 'Null', 'No', 'Faint illusion', '3', '12,700 gp', 'Null', 'Forge Ring, disguise self, invisibility', 'Null', 'Null', '&lt;div topic=&quot;Chameleon Power&quot; level=&quot;8&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Chameleon Power:&lt;/b&gt; As a free action, the wearer of this ring can gain the ability to magically blend in with the surroundings. This provides a +10 competence bonus on her Hide checks. As a standard action, she can also command the ring to utilize the spell &lt;i&gt;disguise self&lt;/i&gt; as often as she wants.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Faint illusion; CL 3rd; Forge Ring, &lt;i&gt;disguise self&lt;/i&gt;,  &lt;i&gt;invisibility&lt;/i&gt;; Price 12,700 gp.&lt;/p&gt;
